{"tid":1587427,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【獨家】9.21元朗克警拖「守護孩子」成員入後巷踢腰 私刑醜聞罪證確鑿！","createTime":"2019-09-22T11:36:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T12:40:46.000Z","uid":68738,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"f70eed59a4d33c62d135641d725cdc8d3524b0c0","tid":1587427,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T11:36:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190922/large/1569148425_a618.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190922%2Flarge%2F1569148425_a618.jpg&h=84d4d33e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n該名男子被制服後本來已經沒甚麼反應，看似失去意識，「奄奄一息咁樣」。(讀者提供圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190922/large/1569148425_1c78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190922%2Flarge%2F1569148425_1c78.jpg&h=d04d3a9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n該名男子被警察踢一腳後，他的身體也沒有反應。(讀者提供圖片)<br />\n<br />\n昨晚（21日）在元朗鳳攸北街一帶，警方截查及拘捕多名市民。警察故意將部份人士由大街帶到後巷，並在巷尾設立封鎖線，拒絕記者進入，避開傳媒監察。不過，有附近居民向《蘋果》提供片段，顯示警察制服一名市民後，一度用腳踢向他，直到發現有人拍攝後，才收斂起來。<br />\n<br />\n昨晚約10時，警察在鳳攸北街截查至少2名年輕人。記者在現場拍攝期間，警察突然把年輕人帶到後巷。大批防暴警察再在巷尾設立封鎖線，將所有傳媒阻隔在約十多米外，又故意以強光閃燈照向記者鏡頭，阻撓拍攝，令傳媒無法看清楚警察在後巷內的行為。其後警方傳媒聯絡隊及速龍小隊增援，情況再變得混亂，記者目睹，一名身穿橙黃色背心的「守護孩子」男成員被警察按在地上制服後，再被大力拖行到後巷。<br />\n<br />\n旁邊大廈的住客Winnie向《蘋果》表示，當時她立即走上大廈平台，於高位觀察後巷及拍攝影片，清楚見到警方完全制服了一名「守護孩子行動」成員後，有警察仍然用腳踢他的腰部。Winnie解釋，見到該名男子被制服後本來已經沒甚麼反應，看似失去意識，「奄奄一息咁樣」，所以被警察踢了一腳後，他的身體也沒有反應。<br />\n<br />\n從影片可見，警察踢了該名男子後，Winnie大叫「喂，影住你呀」。後巷的警察則立即以電筒強光向上射向Winnie阻撓拍攝，並回應說「拍乜X嘢呀」。Winnie表示，警察當時不斷辱罵她是「曱甴」，又說「落嚟呀，咁夠薑，驚呀？」更一度威脅說要上去平台拘捕她，但警員知道正有鏡頭拍攝自己後，行為的確有稍為收斂。Winnie最後等到救護員前來把男子救走後，才離開平台，並無被警方拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n好鄰舍北區教會於facebook發帖，確認有一名「守護孩子行動」成員被捕，現時已送入博愛醫院接受診治。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190922/60072594\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190922%2F60072594&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBlDApO%2Br9QW7Zx2priNtVuo%3D&h=5b396bbb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190922%2F60072594&h=6610fde1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190922/60072594</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78bed166d94b76cb7066ee5e090fd5a7272f0f14","tid":1587427,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T11:37:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"177825fefd7e9d8fa5eb536f3f77c4b5c8e23392","tid":1587427,"uid":68738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T11:38:01.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲有呢位義士既最新消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3c6b4853a21acb76f45b66acf9f9514cf9930b4","tid":1587427,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T11:38:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ed3d151bc205a6370ab24b722a3e562e0da1e0","tid":1587427,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T11:39:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35beded79de0